data.description: Welcome to this charming two-story home nestled in the picturesque community of Village Rowanshyre! Boasting four spacious bedrooms and three bathrooms, this move-in ready residence offers comfortable living spaces and modern amenities for its lucky new owners. Inside, you'll find a well-appointed kitchen with ample cabinetry and countertop space, perfect for preparing meals and entertaining guests. The inviting living areas provide plenty of room for relaxation and gatherings, while the cozy bedrooms offer peaceful retreats at the end of the day. Conveniently located, this home is just minutes away from shopping, dining, parks, and top-rated schools, making it ideal for families and commuters alike. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this lovely property your own!
